UNPATCHABOMB [v1023 - THE AGGRESSIVE FIX]
- UI FINDER: Now recursively scans DEEP into the GUI hierarchy to find the TextBox. No more "UI Not Found".
- TYPING ENGINE: Switched from VirtualInput to Direct .Text manipulation. It is instant and reliable.
- LOADING SPEED: Optimized dictionary parser. It loads in milliseconds, not seconds.
- CRASH PROTECTION: Every Status update is wrapped in pcall. No more nil errors.
]]--

